data.description: Remarks: This custom built home is located on 3.11 Acres with Drew Creek running through the property in the coveted Double Arrow Ranch Community.  It is just seconds from the Double Arrow Golf Course and Lodge and only minutes from Salmon and Seeley Lake.  Enjoy the open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, each with double sinks, a spacious pantry and laundry room with additional sink. The kitchen comes with a gas range, custom built cabinets and quaint dining area for the family to gather. A gas fireplace warms the living room while tall Pella Windows with custom blinds allow you to take in the outdoor views. A large loft serves as a bonus room or additional space. Double car garage, gorgeous composite deck with gas piped in for your bbq, home audio throughout home. This home has it ALL
